=== Match Start ===
Rohit Sharma is batting at the crease.
Jasprit Bumrah is bowling from the crease.
Hardik Pandya is batting or bowling as needed.

=== Batting Stats ===
Rohit Sharma: 45 runs, 75.0% SR
Hardik Pandya: 28 runs, 1 wicket(s)

=== Bowling Stats ===
Jasprit Bumrah: 1 wickets, 8.0 economy

=== Scorers in Match ===
Total runs: 45
Total runs: 28
*/
